* This project is a Next.js app with Supabase backend.
* It builds and runs in a Docker container.
* A database schema is defined in `migrations/create-db.sql`.
* A test suite is defined in `tests/supabase/test-runner.ts`.
* Supabase configuration is defined in NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL
* a Supabase connection string is defined in SUPABASE_DB_URL
* always connect with the remote Supabase database
* if you need to see .env.local just use 'cat .env.local'
